         2. Interactive Dashboard (SPA Core): 
            - Sidebar/Top Nav: Navigates between "Thinking Logic", "Structure Blueprint", "Material Integration", and "Scoring Radar".
            - Main View: Dynamic content area that changes based on selection.
         3. Modules:
            - Scoring Radar: Visualizes what graders look for (Viewpoint, Logic, Structure, Language).
            - Structure Builder: Interactive "Five-Paragraph" model. Clicking sections reveals templates/rules.
            - Material Decoder: A "Before & After" interactive comparison for processing source materials.
         4. Rationale: Exam preparation requires shifting between high-level strategy (Logic) and concrete execution (Format). This structure allows linear learning or targeted review. 
    -->
